fab.com\\/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers\\/\"}' style=\"height:60px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"escalier-quart-tournant\">Escalier quart tournant</h3>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers\\/\"}' class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:49% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img data-attachment-id=\"5513\" data-permalink=\"/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?fit=1575%2C2100&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1575,2100\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?fit=225%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?fit=750%2C1000&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"750\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?resize=750%2C1000&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5513 size-full\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?resize=768%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?resize=225%2C300&amp;ssl=1 225w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?resize=1152%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1152w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?resize=1536%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?resize=900%2C1200&amp;ssl=1 900w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?resize=600%2C800&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?resize=300%2C400&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?resize=150%2C200&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?resize=1200%2C1600&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?resize=1568%2C2091&amp;ssl=1 1568w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1570466469617-0ef03d95baa4.jpg?w=1575&amp;ssl=1 1575w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></figure><div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers\\/\"}' class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>L’escalier quart tournant, en forme de “ L ”, est très <strong>esthétique</strong> et apporte du cachet à un intérieur. </p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-large\"><p>Il permet aussi un gain de place en largeur et en longueur. </p></blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>L’angle du quart tournant peut se situer au départ, à l’arrivée ou au milieu (formant un palier) de l’escalier.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><br>Si vous souhaitez un escalier très <strong>design</strong>, aérien, et qui laisse passer la lumière, optez pour un&nbsp;<em>escalier à limon central quart tournant.</em></p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers\\/\"}' style=\"height:10px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers\\/\"}' class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img data-attachment-id=\"6879\" data-permalink=\"/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers/limons-cremaillere-inversee-acier-escalier-quart-tournant-metal-sur-mesure-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/limons-cremaillere-inversee-acier-escalier-quart-tournant-metal-sur-mesure-1.jpeg?fit=1024%2C705&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1024,705\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"limons-cremaillere-inversee-acier-escalier-quart-tournant-metal-sur-mesure-1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/limons-cremaillere-inversee-acier-escalier-quart-tournant-metal-sur-mesure-1.jpeg?fit=300%2C207&amp;ss