1-1.jpeg?resize=1568%2C980&amp;ssl=1 1568w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/static/335e561c8b0d502ade034e90784525ff/7dfa1de27d_50146041_escalier-droit-tournant1-1.jpeg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></figure></li></ul></figure>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers\\/\"}' style=\"height:61px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"escalier-deux-quarts-tournant\">Escalier deux-quarts tournant</h3>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers\\/\"}' class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img data-attachment-id=\"5509\" data-permalink=\"/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6.jpg?fit=1534%2C2301&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1534,2301\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6.jpg?fit=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6.jpg?fit=683%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6.jpg?resize=683%2C1024&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5509 size-full\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6.jpg?resize=683%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 683w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6.jpg?resize=768%2C1152&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6.jpg?resize=1024%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6.jpg?resize=1365%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1365w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6.jpg?resize=1200%2C1800&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6.jpg?w=1534&amp;ssl=1 1534w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></figure><div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers\\/\"}' class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>L’escalier deux-quarts tournant – aussi appelé&nbsp;<strong>escalier demi tournant</strong>&nbsp;– se compose de deux angles et trois volées de marches. </p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-large\"><p>Il apporte un&nbsp;gain de place maximum, et réduit l’espace utilisé au sol puisqu’il peut se placer dans le coin d’une pièce.</p></blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p><br>Les deux quarts tournant sont répartis sur la montée des marches, ou obtenus grâce à un palier. Ce type d’escalier est très confortable à l’utilisation.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers\\/\"}' style=\"height:10px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers\\/\"}' style=\"height:10px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers\\/\"}' style=\"height:60px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"escalier-helicoidal\">Escalier hélicoïdal</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Un escalier hélicoïdal, aussi appelé&nbsp;<strong>escalier en colimaçon</strong>, est la forme d’escalier qui offre&nbsp;<strong>le plus grand gain de place</strong>&nbsp;puisque les marches s’organisent autour d’une colonne centrale. Il s’installe partout dans un intérieur car il ne nécessite pas d’appui contre un mur. Cependant, il est moins confortable que les autres types d’escaliers, il vous sera impossible d’y transporter des objets de gros volume. Un escalier en colimaçon est souvent utilisé comme&nbsp;<strong>escalier secondaire</strong>&nbsp;et non comme escalier principal.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers\\/\"}' class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img data-attachment-id=\"6884\" data-permalink=\"/comment-choisir-son-escalier-les-differents-types-descaliers/escarmor-escalier_helicoidal_bois_sans_contremarches_teinte_chene_moyen-limon_debillarde_fut_central-poteaux_main_courante_cylindriques-lisses_tubes_inox